{"tid":1363774,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗人為大家介紹下元朗既好飲好食","createTime":"2019-07-25T08:41:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T08:45:49.000Z","uid":255437,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"152aacd0fdfbe037982d915eb2d6f8c10b642e98","tid":1363774,"uid":255437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:41:59.000Z","msg":"大家唔使驚,雖然元朗無警察, 但係我哋有黑社會為我哋維持治安.<br />\n為大家介紹一下元朗嘅好飲好食,希望大家週末入嚟元朗消費,重振元朗經濟<br />\n<br />\n1.元朗YOHO MALL大型Food Court<br />\n<br />\n元朗最大型商場YOHO MALL，全場佔地9,000多呎，場內有12間掃街小食店進駐，提供各式各樣街頭小食，如元朗街坊小店，各地菜式包括中、日、韓、泰等，場內更設有掃碼點餐，客人可以即時點選指定餐廳，再柯打菜式，然後再以八達通付款就完成，相當方便。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但yoho mall係屬於新鴻基, 可能嗰日會唔開,會令大家失望</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r3m9Bfx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr3m9Bfx.jpg&h=cb55ff38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2.B仔涼粉<br />\n<br />\n佳記甜品為老顧客開創的糖水甜品「B仔涼粉」，成了馳名香港的特色甜點，大盆盛裝多樣繽紛水果佐上仙草涼粉，堆疊成一座小山呈現華麗豐盛，視覺與味覺都被滿足了！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> 作為一間無牌食肆竟然可以屹立不到咁多年,背後一定唔會有一股無形嘅勢力幫助緊佢哋</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AbEZYuf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAbEZYuf.jpg&h=3cc70a2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3.牛屎<br />\n牛屎係好罕有,希望你哋星期六你嗰陣可以搵到<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人 727元朗見</span></span>"},{"pid":"5207bc7c49f57f12f1230bb68a886b92bd3333e4","tid":1363774,"uid":255437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:42:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c35b59a3154adbbc36c839c839d685fedf8e6e7d","tid":1363774,"uid":255437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:43:10.000Z","msg":"727 求下你地入嚟元朗消費"},{"pid":"eb783126a59d46908d26a15fab5b9d1f0f958479","tid":1363774,"uid":255437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:43:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"49a53da9273fb0f9f2f36fa7b0dd148a6e787805","tid":1363774,"uid":255437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:43:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fa6777378ae8b913ddbe459b653ffb3bdff45574","tid":1363774,"uid":255437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:43:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0f7c7dd31e6f6347dfc0034ecb4d324f30a2b54c","tid":1363774,"uid":255437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:43:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9e56015ca240755d5ca292eb869347b54efa5031","tid":1363774,"uid":255437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:44:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"822c42d8a037d9156682407b39e12696cb9e53ad","tid":1363774,"uid":255437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:44:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"002ac735fde2b507471e848fc56858727c797e8e","tid":1363774,"uid":255437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:44:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f8ccc38bcf9e2f14c8a873a937a3a89eac5b9d5c","tid":1363774,"uid":255437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:44:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8faca3b0957bfb6a884c95ce4fda12e816eef181","tid":1363774,"uid":255437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:45:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c60732847ae7af17c7d9ecade66d393e99495796","tid":1363774,"uid":255437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:45:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8d2ab8bdedc14368203c364d6565b2b50df9faed","tid":1363774,"uid":255437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:45:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"89da0bce6d14c1d29f4fe6771d0a67dcd882d430","tid":1363774,"uid":57328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:45:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/krvqOzi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkrv